    "description": "Zostel invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Marketplace Manager at our Visakhapatnam location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Zostel:\nZostel is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zostel!",
